Step 1 — Pehli Baar Clone Karna
bashgit clone https://github.com/Hackteachbhai/Pralay-VulX
cd Pralay-VulX

Step 2 — Agar Folder Pehle Se Ho
bashrm -rf Pralay-VulX
git clone https://github.com/Hackteachbhai/Pralay-VulX
cd Pralay-VulX

Step 3 — Tool Run Karna
bash# File ka naam space ke saath hai — quotes zaroori hain
python3 'Added pralay_vulx.py' <target>
Available Flags:
--ports PORTS       Specific ports scan karne ke liye
--crawl-url URL     Ek specific URL crawl karna
--stealth           Stealth mode enable karo
--tor               Traffic Tor se route karo
--no-nmap           Nmap scan skip karo
Example with flags:
bashpython3 'Added pralay_vulx.py' example.com --ports 80,443 --stealth

Step 4 — Latest Update Lena
bashcd Pralay-VulX
git pull origin main

Step 5 — Files Dekhna
bashls -la

